17:00.000Z","msg":"應該15k？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:53:07.000Z","msg":"當你搭老母，去20kg回30kg = 4000HKD<br />\n住business hotel= 5000yen x 15 = 75,000YEN = 5600HKD<br />\n食 早(600) 午(900) 晚(1500) = 3000yen x 15 = 45,000 yen = 3400HKD<br />\n<br />\n唔搭車唔買嘢已經13k<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:背包窮遊嘅話一日&lt;10,000yen都冇問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:01:37.000Z","msg":"如果一個人淨係去八日到？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:14:11.000Z","msg":"其實好難一概而論<br />\n因為變數最大嘅車費同購物，每個人嘅預算真係差天共地<br />\n例如京都市內搭足一日巴士車費只係600yen，而同樣係一日，立山黑部車費就要成萬yen<br />\n我自己去，唔shopping嘅話購物預算&lt;3000yen，但買起上嚟都用10幾萬yen<br />\n連瞓都有分&lt;3000yen嘅膠囊/青旅同&gt;10000yen嘅旅館<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你唔係戶口冇乜錢剩都要去旅行嘅話，建議你直頭唔好理預算<br />\n換住15萬yen唔夠就到時去7仔ATM拎算啦"},{"pid":"6eb88ba5750aad46a60f9760a07b49041ca202f3","tid":1472743,"uid":2161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82ac736468cd2a57a5ae4aaf9629e2e105272be3","tid":1472743,"uid":168010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfb12b55fc3dab27598ec5d0209f186c8cb549b3","tid":1472743,"uid":2161,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:18:05.000Z","msg":"半個月假玩日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係你就星馬泰算啦1皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:48:35.000Z","msg":"1皮去星?<br />\n你似玩9樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:20:16.000Z","msg":"講真星加坡即日來回都得啦 住返馬拉平好多既<br />\n不過都係去泰國做大爺咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1萬要機+宿講真係咩錢啊仲要去半個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><